<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="live-adj">live <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /laɪv/    美 /laɪv/  </p>
<p>[常用于名词前]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-living">1.★ <strong>活的；有生命的 (living)</strong></h4>
<p>反 dead </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We were so excited to see <strong>real live</strong> elephants.
我们看到活生生的大象非常兴奋。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>现场直播的；现场表演的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We watched the football match on live television. 
我们看了电视现场直播的足球赛。</p></div></div>